			<article class="entry hentry post-150921 post type-post status-publish category-showcase tag-diversify-photo tag-lewis-brent-photographer tag-mentors tag-minorities tag-news-and-news-media-2 tag-newspapers tag-photography tag-race-and-ethnicity per-lewis-brent-photographer des-mentors des-minorities des-news-and-news-media des-newspapers des-photography des-race-and-ethnicity org-diversify-photo news_keywords-mentor news_keywords-minorities news_keywords-newspaper news_keywords-photography" id="post-150921">
